title: About me
text: I’m a former athlete turned coach who is looking to leave the gym and get a real job.

title: Ilona Silverwood
text: I will eventually write instructions on how to set up a Quarto website, but right now the process involves a lot of trial and error. I also have occassional moments of overconfidence where I think I know what I’m doing without referring to the documentation, which results in subsequently spending lots of time reading documentation to figure out what I did wrong.

title: Ilona Silverwood
text: To learn more about Quarto websites from people who actually know what they’re doing, visit https://quarto.org/docs/websites.
